David's dwm build
=================

My own, somewhat opinionated, build of the dwm window manager, patched
to suit my own needs.

Dependencies
============

Aside from the usual dependencies for dwm, this build needs the following
software in order to run as it is configured. Pretty much all of this can
be changed in the config.def.h.

 -	Terminal emulator - ghostty
 -	Web browser - firefox
 -	Launcher menu - rofi
 -	Notification daemon - dunst
 -	Wallpaper setting - nitrogen
 -	Compositor - picom

 Patches
 =======

 The following patches have been applied, in order:

 -	alpha (transparency in the title bar)
 -	xrdb (define colorscheme in .Xresources)
 	- requires modification of the xrdb() function to include alphas
 -	cfacts-vanitygaps

